        "TileImage": "$($repository 8397ae00-384f-4a78-aef0-82ed48d7869d).Image",
        "Description": "Good job in Colombia. Our new batch of targets are in the nearby country of Argentina, as more of Stepanovich&apos;s henchmen are residing there to prepare for an exchange of information. Just to add a bit of difficulty, we ask that you kill our first target through his favorite activity: wine drinking.\r\rThe other three are up for grabs in any manner you see fit. Good luck.\r\r-Eclipse",
